ANN — All the News You Need
===========================

Original concept and premise
----------------------------
The idea behind this project — a tiny daily news digest built on the premise
that news consumption is not a civic virtue, and that most people do not need
to follow the news to be well-informed — originates with **ulyssestenn**.

  Original repository: https://github.com/ulyssestenn/allthenewsyouneed

The premise text, the selection standard, and the digest format described in
this repository derive from that original work. Full rights and credit for the
original idea are reserved to its author. This repository is an independent
implementation that codes what is described in the original project's Markdown
specification.

