Third-party sources
-------------------
Headlines are fetched from the public RSS feeds of the respective outlets
(WSJ, NYT, NBC) and, for AP, from a Google News site-scoped query. All
headline text and links remain the property of their respective publishers and
are used here only to reference and link to the original reporting.
